parameters:
\SE[2]I took care of it beforehand. I'm a thoughtful woman,
aren't I?
\SE[0]Is it okay? I'm a refined young lady, right?

P-Please... help me! If I stay like this, that person in the
back will violate me...

\SE[2]Before you ask, let me say this first. I don't have
the time or ability to help anyone other than you all.

Well, maybe men together wouldn't be so bad after all? I
think everyone has their own way of expressing love.

\SE[0]Mhm, mhm... The form of love is different for each
person, right...!

Just leave me alone... I'll be here until I die anyway...
Ugh...

If I can escape from here... I...! I intend to marry that
person.

At first, I didn't understand why he was coming on to me,
another guy... But then I realized that he was the first
person who truly understood me.

\SE[74]Huh... well, I don't really care, but \SE[51]well, I
guess it's not necessarily a bad thing...?
Prisoner with Feelings for a Partner

If I can go back to the outside world... I will change. I
will work hard for the sake of building a family with that
person.
Uu... Why am I in a place like this...?

Hehe... What's the matter, two cute little kittens...? If
you stay in a place like this, a scary wolf might just come
and chomp!... and eat you, you know...?
\SE[50]The dog in the cage isn't barking, you know.
Oh... I don't dislike strong-willed women...

So there was a woman after all... She had a... nice scent...
I could smell it...

\SE[52]There are only these kinds of people here, huh? Let's
go quickly.

W-Wait! I'm going to be executed soon! Just a little... Let
me smell your scent...

\SE[4]Don't be fooled. There are no death row prisoners in
this prison.
S-Sorry... Your angry face is cute, you know...? Hehehe...

Hehe... You're all beautiful, aren't you... If only there
wasn't this cage, I could have treated you kindly... Hehe...

\SE[4]Go ahead and give it a try. \!\SE[3]I'll tear apart
that pathetic thing for you.

That girl with black hair over there... She's so lovely... I
want to dedicate my whole life to her...

\SE[18]...It's their own fault for picking a fight with the
wrong person.

\SE[90]W-Well...these things happen sometimes. \.We just
need to clean up quickly.
